    "description": "We are excited to introduce our new application, AniCursor - a tool specifically designed for creating animated cursors. With AniCursor, you can either download ready-made cursors from the Steam Workshop or create your own using our unique editor.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAniCursor offers you a wide range of useful features that enhance the cursor creation experience. You can easily find the cursor you need with the search function, create cursors from GIF animations or simple PNG images, adjust the selection area, and customize other parameters.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAdditional, AniCursor provides access to an extensive library of ready-made animated cursors available in the Steam Workshop. You can choose and install cursors from the Steam Workshop or even contribute your own sets to the workshop, allowing you to share them with other users.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDon't wait any longer - join our community and start creating impressive animated cursors with AniCursor today!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe look forward to seeing you in our community!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChoose the best cursor for you =)",
